1637
01:56:01,265 --> 01:56:03,132
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Me dê as chaves, por favor.</font></b>

1638
01:56:10,830 --> 01:56:12,230
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Vou checar.</font></b>

1639
01:56:24,459 --> 01:56:27,004
<b><font color=#FFFF00>- Tudo certo.
- Por favor.</font></b>

1640
01:56:43,041 --> 01:56:44,412
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Pare.</font></b>

1641
01:56:45,092 --> 01:56:46,492
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Vou checar.</font></b>

1642
01:56:57,133 --> 01:56:58,433
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Nada.</font></b>

1643
01:57:03,205 --> 01:57:04,585
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Pare.</font></b>

1644
01:57:18,461 --> 01:57:20,361
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Tem um cadeado
nesta última.</font></b>

1645
01:57:21,067 --> 01:57:22,429
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Você tem a chave?</font></b>

1646
01:57:23,630 --> 01:57:25,163
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Sr. Baker.</font></b>

1647
01:57:25,606 --> 01:57:27,060
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Está com ele.</font></b>

1648
01:57:27,942 --> 01:57:29,542
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Está no chaveiro.</font></b>

1649
01:57:47,126 --> 01:57:48,426
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Não encontrei nada.</font></b>

1650
01:57:51,845 --> 01:57:53,543
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Vamos subir.</font></b>

1651
01:58:01,149 --> 01:58:02,534
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Sente-se.</font></b>

1652
01:58:05,155 --> 01:58:07,155
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Vasculhamos.
