01:58:15,039 --> 01:58:16,439
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Sim, me importo.</font></b>

1656
01:58:16,799 --> 01:58:18,199
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Ela tem 9 anos.</font></b>

1657
01:58:20,354 --> 01:58:22,754
<b><font color=#FFFF00>Prefere
